fat hen
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:[Var. <i>Chenopodium</i> spp., esp. as eaten as vegetables: earliest recorded occurrence.] <i>Chenopodium</i> spp. Also with distinguishing epithets. Also called  goosefoot (transl. of <i>Chenopodium</i>.  =white fat hen, =goose foot, =red fathen ex</i> which are eaten as vegetables.
